MR. BECK ASKS THAT ALL CELLS

11:25.268 --> 11:29.648
BE HANDED TO THE SECURITY STAFF

11:29.730 --> 11:31.732
FOR THE DURATION

11:29.730 --> 11:31.732
OF THE CHALLENGE. THANK YOU.

