THESE SIMPLETONS WILL CHEAT.

11:39.157 --> 11:42.452
THEY'LL USE ANY TRICK

11:39.157 --> 11:42.452
TO GET THE EDGE, MR. GORDON.

11:42.494 --> 11:44.496
THEY ALL HATE ME, YOU KNOW.

11:44.538 --> 11:47.541
A GREAT MAN IS KNOWN

11:44.538 --> 11:47.541
BY HIS ENEMIES.

11:47.582 --> 11:49.668
PRECISELY, MISS SUMAC.

11:49.708 --> 11:52.711
ONLY TWO KINDS IN THE WORLD --

11:49.708 --> 11:52.711
ONLY TWO --

11:52.753 --> 11:54.130
THE CATTLE

11:54.172 --> 11:59.260
AND THE PEOPLE

11:54.172 --> 11:59.260
WHO LIKE A REALLY GOOD STEAK.

11:59.302 --> 12:02.763
I'M GONNA GO MAKE

