A FEW PHONE CALLS...

12:02.805 --> 12:05.266
IF I HAVE TO TURN OVER

12:02.805 --> 12:05.266
MY LIFELINE. [ CHUCKLES ]

12:05.308 --> 12:07.561
OH, AND I'VE GOT TO GET

12:05.308 --> 12:07.561
INTO MY COSTUME.

12:07.602 --> 12:10.104
I'M AFRAID WE'RE ABANDONING YOU,

12:07.602 --> 12:10.104
MISS SUMAC.

12:10.146 --> 12:13.441
I WILL SURVIVE, MR. BECK,

