SOME OF YOUR GUESTS

12:13.483 --> 12:17.736
SEEM VERY DETERMINED.

12:17.778 --> 12:19.155
THESE PLODDERS --

12:19.197 --> 12:21.491
I'M SURPRISED IF THEY CAN EVEN

12:19.197 --> 12:21.491
SPELL THEIR OWN NAME.

