TAKE YOUR HAND OFF ME.

12:47.601 --> 12:50.437
I'M JUST PASSING ON

12:47.601 --> 12:50.437
SOME FRIENDLY ADVICE.

12:50.478 --> 12:53.147
YOU DON'T WANT TO BE IN BED

12:50.478 --> 12:53.147
WITH BECK.

12:53.189 --> 12:55.692
GUY LIKE THAT

12:53.189 --> 12:55.692
MAKES A  LOT  OF ENEMIES.

12:55.734 --> 12:58.069
SOMEBODY'S BOUND TO GET HURT.

12:58.111 --> 13:00.779
YOU MIGHT WANT TO TAKE A WALK

12:58.111 --> 13:00.779
ABOUT NOW, MARCO.

13:00.821 --> 13:02.907
