ELECTRICITY BUZZES ]

13:04.242 --> 13:05.702
YEAH.

13:05.744 --> 13:07.412
YEAH, SURE.

13:07.454 --> 13:09.205
COME ON, BOYS.

13:11.750 --> 13:12.875
SORRY ABOUT THAT.

13:12.917 --> 13:14.586
AND YOU ARE?

13:14.628 --> 13:16.504
I'M RAY HAMMETT, SALEM P.D.

13:16.546 --> 13:18.715
I'M SORRY.

13:16.546 --> 13:18.715
I-I-I'M NOT FAMILIAR

13:18.757 --> 13:20.133
WITH THAT CHARACTER.

13:20.174 --> 13:22.218
OH, UH [Chuckling] NO.

13:20.174 --> 13:22.218
NO, MA'AM.

13:22.260 --> 13:23.886
UH, I'M THE REAL DEAL.

13:23.928 --> 13:25.513
MORRIS BECK PULLS A LOT OF WATER

13:25.555 --> 13:27.223
WITH THE CITY FATHERS

13:25.555 --> 13:27.223
IN THIS TOWN,

13:27.265 --> 13:29.100
SO HIS EVENTS

13:27.265 --> 13:29.100
MERIT A POLICE PRESENCE.

13:29.142 --> 13:31.311
SECOND YEAR IN A ROW

13:29.142 --> 13:31.311
I PULLED THE SHORT STRAW.

13:31.352 --> 13:35.649
AND SO YOU -- YOU, WHAT --

13:31.352 --> 13:35.649
YOU STAND IN A CORNER WATCHING

13:35.690 --> 13:37.609
LIKE A REFEREE?

13:37.651 --> 13:39.818
YEAH, SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

13:39.860 --> 13:41.904
ONLY, UM...

13:41.946 --> 13:45.784
I DON'T  HAVE  TO STAND

13:41.946 --> 13:45.784
IN THE CORNER.

13:53.124 --> 13:55.126
